    {
      "id": "btQ4Nq5ZS5NXmsxtnLj--",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 27874.98369852447,
      "y": 2111.257017220203,
      "width": 860.5386352539062,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 4,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bMc",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 71761495,
      "version": 896,
      "versionNonce": 541696441,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775751727956,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\n\n\nThis area is for List of emails - The list of emails displaying here will be filtered by:  1. Suppliers\nrequested in the RFP...2. Customer's Company Name...3. Supplier quote due date from the RFP\n\nThe Filter controls will allow the user to widen the filter/search parameters so that more or less\nemails will appear here.  Ultimately the goal in filtering emails is so we can capture the emails\ncontaining energy quotes from the suppliers for the given customer.  (independently scrollable)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "dDWpr4uidwjuF1SR94RKd",
      "originalText": "\n\n\nThis area is for List of emails - The list of emails displaying here will be filtered by:  1. Suppliers requested in the RFP...2. Customer's Company Name...3. Supplier quote due date from the RFP\n\nThe Filter controls will allow the user to widen the filter/search parameters so that more or less emails will appear here.  Ultimately the goal in filtering emails is so we can capture the emails containing energy quotes from the suppliers for the given customer.  (independently scrollable)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
