      "versionNonce": 1073952379,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775756680152,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "This section will contain a table that will receive the values submitted\nfrom the controls directly above this section.\n\nThe column headers will be:  Supplier, a Contract Term column for\neach unique term length submitted (no duplications)\n\nEach row beneath will have the supplier name and then the submitted\nEnergy rate in the appropriate Contract Term column.\n\nWithin this table, the user will have the ability to click to highlight a\ncell containing an energy rate under a given contract term (only one\nhighlighted cell per column)\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "WOiQYHRVH5jRlYqUdnda5",
      "originalText": "This section will contain a table that will receive the values submitted from the controls directly above this section.\n\nThe column headers will be:  Supplier, a Contract Term column for each unique term length submitted (no duplications)\n\nEach row beneath will have the supplier name and then the submitted  Energy rate in the appropriate Contract Term column.\n\nWithin this table, the user will have the ability to click to highlight a cell containing an energy rate under a given contract term (only one highlighted cell per column)\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
